  "description": "A close-up, symmetrical view of the center of a tulip flower. The petals are a blend of vibrant red and soft white, radiating outwards from a bright yellow core.  Within the yellow center are six dark, almost black, anthers surrounding a pale pink pistil. The lighting highlights the textured surfaces of the petals and the pollen-dusted anthers. The depth of field is shallow, focusing sharply on the flower's reproductive parts.",
